'''Konstantinos''' is the name of a practicing [[occultism|occultist]] and [[neopagan]] (born 1972), and the author of six [[Supernatural|spiritual]] and [[occult]] books on nocturnal witchcraft, all published by [[Llewellyn Worldwide]].  Konstantinos has a bachelor's degree in English and technical writing. He lives in New York.

Konstantinos has been working on [[occult]] and [[paranormal]] topics for over fifteen years. He has been a guest on various shows and documentaries.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.llewellyn.com/author_interview.php?author_id=3225&interview_id=62|title=Llewellyn Worldwide - Interview with Konstantinos|website=www.llewellyn.com|access-date=2017-07-24}}</ref> He has also written numerous articles over the years. He recently appeared on ''[[Coast to Coast AM]]'' hosted by [[George Noory]].<ref>George, Noory, and Konstantinos, Rowley, perf. "The Occult." Coast to Coast AM. Premier Radio Networks, 23 July 2007. web. 11 Dec 2012. <http://www.coasttocoastam.com/show/2007/07/23>.</ref>

